{"id":168110,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/07/译者-《译者》每日原文推荐-2011721/","date":"2011-07-22T06:30:25Z","modified":"2011-07-22T07:53:10Z","title":"译者 | 《译者》每日原文推荐  2011/7/21","content":"<p><p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以下为每日原文推荐。如果你有兴趣，请参与翻译并将译文寄给</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《译者》</span></a><b>(</b><span><b><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"mailto:iyizhe@gmail.com\"><span>iyizhe@gmail.com</span></a>)</span></b></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以便与大家共享。欢迎使用</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feedburner.google.com/fb/a/mailverify?uri=yizhe&#038;loc=en_US\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">邮件组</span></a><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">、</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://goo.gl/f1NDK\">Google Reader</a><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">和推特（</span><span><span>@yigroup</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，</span></span><span><span>@xiaomi2020</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）跟踪我们的最新消息。</span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【时政热点】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">外交学者：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://the-diplomat.com/2011/07/21/chinese-foreign-policy-after-hu/?utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+the-diplomat+%28The+Diplomat+RSS%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">胡锦涛之后的中国外交政策</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——明年中国更换领导人之后，外交政策是否会出现巨变？历史表明很有可能</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《每日电讯报》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/apple/8652295/Apple-HP-and-Dell-among-companies-responsible-for-electronic-sweatshops-claims-report.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">苹果、惠普和戴尔都对中国的电子血汗工厂负有责任</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国劳工观察的报告显示，这些公司间接导致了中国工人的自杀</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《经济学人》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.economist.com/node/18988926?story_id=18988926&#038;fsrc=rss\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国的人口：形只影单</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国人口最多的省份对独生子女政策提出了公开的批评</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《商业周刊》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.businessweek.com/magazine/chinese-cities-risky-borrowing-binge-07212011.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国地方城市危险的借债扩建</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——尽管土地估价和市场需求都很成问题，地方城市仍在在大建特建</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">路透社：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/07/21/us-china-bonds-idUSTRE76K0JJ20110721?feedType=RSS&#038;feedName=Yuan&#038;virtualBrandChannel=11721&#038;utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+reuters%2FUSyuanNews+%28News+%2F+US+%2F+YUAN+GCA%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">地方政府债务警讯可能会使中国地方债券改革被耽搁</span></a></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">路透社：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://old.news.yahoo.com/s/nm/20110721/bs_nm/us_imf_china\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">国际货币基金说中国的房地产泡沫令人担忧</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——尽管中国采取了一些措施抑制房价上涨，减少房屋交易，但泡沫依然存在</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《商业周刊》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.businessweek.com/news/2011-07-21/china-links-fast-nuclear-reactor-to-grid-after-40-year-research.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国将研制</span>40<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">年的新型核电反应炉并网</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——这种仍在实验中的新型反应炉比现有装置的辐射更少</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《温哥华太阳报》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.vancouversun.com/business/Beijing+outclasses+London+managing+Murdoch/5129528/story.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">在控制默多克方面，北京比伦敦更高一筹</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国将默多克玩弄于股掌之上的技巧，令西方艳羡不已</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《外交政策》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.foreignpolicy.com/articles/2011/07/21/sorry_pakistan_china_is_no_sugar_daddy\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">抱歉，巴基斯坦，中国并非傻大款</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——仅仅由于美国和巴基斯坦闹僵，并不意味着中国想要取而代之</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">外交学者：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://the-diplomat.com/china-power/2011/07/21/china-encircles-india/?utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+the-diplomat+%28The+Diplomat+RSS%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国包围印度</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——尽管印度可以与美国套近乎，但是面对中巴联手，仍然会为自己受到包围而苦恼</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【经贸动向】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美联社：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://old.news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20110721/ap_on_bi_ge/as_china_manufacturing\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">调查显示中国的制造业发展出现下降</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——汇丰银行调查的采购经理指数跌至</span><span>28</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">个月来最低，显示制造业出现萎缩</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国法律博客：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.chinalawblog.com/2011/07/factory_closings_in_south_china_all_part_of_the_plan.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国南部的工厂关门，这是在计划之中的事情</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国的十二五规划定出了中国经济转型的新目标，南方一些劳动密集型工厂倒闭是意料之中</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《商业周刊》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.businessweek.com/news/2011-07-21/apple-surpasses-lenovo-revenue-in-china-on-strength-of-iphones.html\">iPhone<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">热销，使苹果在华销售额超过联想</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——在</span><span>iPhone</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">上市两年后，苹果在华业绩即超过联想，但苹果表示这只是个开始</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【社会百态】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《旺报》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.wantchinatimes.com/news-subclass-cnt.aspx?cid=1103&#038;MainCatID=11&#038;id=20110720000006\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">裸婚反映出中国青年面临的挑战</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——当今年轻人要实现自己的中国梦，需要面临严酷的现实和飞涨的成本</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《大西洋》月刊：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.theatlantic.com/life/archive/2011/07/are-vegetables-and-exercise-causing-obesity-in-china/242269/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">吃素和锻炼让中国的孩子发胖？</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——有研究结果表明，那些令美国人更健康的活动对其他国家可能并非如此</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《商业周刊》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.businessweek.com/magazine/chinese-partying-is-a-boon-for-chauffeurs-07212011.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国人的吃喝玩乐使得代驾司机成为热门</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——去年中国抓到了</span><span>52</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">万酒后驾驶的司机。新的法规使得更多的人需求代驾服务</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><i>友情提示：您可以到<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/\">这里</a>看到推友们对该篇译文的评论和转发；欢迎参与！如果您的电脑可以翻墙，请到<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/\">这里</a>的左栏参加我们的一个小调查</i><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5425822223623422432-4971554353657643840?l=yyyyiiii.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":776,"categories":[1],"tags":[8840]}